Commentary Text: Rabada to Uthappa, out Caught by Pant!! Commentary Text: Prasidh to Prithvi Shaw, out Caught by Karthik!! Terrific catch by a flying DK! Excellent delivery too. Short of a length around off and jags away a tad. Shaw tries to defend it off his back foot, gets squared up somewhat and gets a thick outside edge. The KKR skipper flies to his right and plucks it out of thin air. Not for the first time have we seen him take such a blinder. Quite an eventful over that. 17 runs and a wicket to cap it off. Prithvi Shaw c Karthik b Prasidh 14(7) [6s-2]

Commentary Text: Prasidh to Dhawan, no run, KKR review! Has Dhawan nicked it? Or did it come off the jersey? There was a certain sound but don't think it came off the willow. Or is it the trouser? Waiting for the replays. There's a spike on UltraEdge but not sure whether it's the inside edge or off the trousers. A tough call for the third umpire. No conclusive evidence and the onfield decision stays. KKR have lost their only review. A short delivery that was angled into the batsman, Dhawan was looking to block it as the ball brushed his trouser and settled into the keeper's gloves
